text: Pizza was delicious, service was extremely slow and the delivery driver got lost. I ordered the pizzas 3 hour ahead of when I wanted them delivered. When I called to see why the pizzas were late I was told they were just going in the oven. The delivery was scheduled for 6:45 yet arrived at 7:35. Way too late.

name: Gwen Hennessy
text: Decently priced, tasty buffet pizza. Good hours for the lunch buffet (11am-2pm). Does get busy around noon, go early for the best selection.

text: Havent seen  a round table pizza since I was a university of Washington alum - and so after doing a little shopping at Victoria Secret, wandered in here, and still had tghe best salad bar I ever remember. Staff was pleasant. Environment was nostalgic vintage Roundtable. Very good. Nice staff!

name: Matthew Medina
text: Growing up in California, pizza was either Straw Hat or Round Table, and to this day Round Table always carries with it a little taste of home. What sets Round Table apart for me are the toppings which are always fresh and delicious, and the crust is light and just the right amount of crispiness.
